# &quot;Alstonia penangiana&quot; - Penang Hill in Malaysia
# &quot;Alstonia pneumatophora&quot; - W Malaysia, Borneo, Sulawesi, Sumatra 
# &quot;Alstonia quaternata&quot; New Caledonia
# &quot;Alstonia rostrata&quot; - Yunnan, Indochina, W Malaysia, Sumatra
# &quot;Alstonia rubiginosa&quot; - Papua New Guinea
# &quot;Alstonia rupestris&quot; - Thailand
# &quot;Alstonia scholaris&quot; – pali-mari, dita bark, bitter bark, milkwood, milky bean, milky pine, white cheesewood, scholar tree, blackboard tree - E + S + SE Asia, Papuasia, N Australia
# &quot;Alstonia sebusii&quot; - Yunnan, Bhutan, Assam, N Myanmar
# &quot;Alstonia spatulata&quot; – hard milkwood, Siamese balsa - SE Asia, New Guinea
# &quot;Alstonia spectabilis&quot; – poele bark, jackapple, leatherjacket, milky yellowwood - SE Asia, Papuasia, N Australia
# &quot;Alstonia sphaerocapitata&quot; - New Caledonia
# &quot;Alstonia venenata&quot; - S India
