* &quot;Magnified and Reduced by Inches&quot; / &quot;Pablo y Zelda&quot; (1997, Jade Tree Records)
* &quot;All Your Friends Are Comedians&quot; / &quot;The Great Salt Lake&quot; (1998, Mag Wheel Records)
* Juno &amp; The Dismemberment Plan (2000, DeSoto Records)
